RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Yelm, WA operates under a Mayor-Council government. The Mayor is elected at-large, and the City Council consists of seven members also elected at-large. The terms for council members are staggered four-year terms. David Johnstone was appointed to Position 6 on May 27, 2025, and Stephanie Kangiser was appointed to Position 4 in March 2024.
